snippet.description:
This is a FAN/CONCEPT/PARODY FAN TRAILER. It's not an official or real FAN TRAILER. It's made for entertainment purposes only.

The inspiration behind this video: 

Will Eleven get another chance at defeating Vecna? Is Max going to wake up? Can Will ever find peace in his life? These were just some of my biggest questions going into Stranger Things season 5, Volume 1. Seeing as it has been over three years since Stranger Things season 4's ending, my list of lingering questions has become overwhelmingly long. But I guess good things do come to those who wait, because Volume 1's four episodes quickly answer some of my most burning questions.

Set a year and a half after the events of season 4, Stranger Things season 5 finds Hawkins under military control following the "earthquake" that tore apart the town, which was actually caused by Vecna. The villain hasn't been seen since he was thrown from a window with a shotgun blast, but that hasn't stopped the group from staying ready for Vecna's next move. While Hopper and Joyce are helping Eleven train, Mike, Will, Dustin, Lucas, Nancy, Jonathan, Steve, and Robin coordinate ways to locate Vecna. Max is still present, but she remains in a coma, serving as a reminder about how high the stakes are.

Thank You So Much For Watching!
Stay Tuned! Stay Buzzed!

──────────────────

snippet.title: STRANGER THINGS 5: VOLUME 2 | TRAILER (2025) | Netflix
snippet.description:
#Netflix #StrangerThings #StrangerThings5

🎥 Attention viewers! (ITS FAN MADE)
Experience the beginning of the end with this Stranger Things Season 5 VOLUME 2 Trailer, bringing a final look at the epic conclusion to Netflix’s biggest series. Featuring fan-favorite characters like Eleven (Millie Bobby Brown), Mike Wheeler (Finn Wolfhard), Will Byers (Noah Schnapp), Lucas (Caleb McLaughlin), Max (Sadie Sink), Dustin (Gaten Matarazzo), Robin (Maya Hawke), Steve Harrington (Joe Keery), Nancy (Natalia Dyer), Jonathan (Charlie Heaton), Joyce Byers (Winona Ryder), and Chief Hopper (David Harbour), the final season sets the stage for a showdown with Vecna (Jamie Campbell Bower). This concept trailer captures the tone of the Stranger Things Season 5 Official Teaser, Final Season Trailer 2, and all the emotional stakes fans have been waiting for as Netflix’s iconic story reaches its climactic end.

The inspiration behind this video:
The long-awaited Stranger Things Season 5 VOLUME 2 Trailer has arrived, giving fans their deepest look yet at the final chapter of Netflix’s biggest phenomenon. As the Stranger Things Season 5 story pushes toward its epic conclusion, the new footage expands on what we saw in the Stranger Things 5 Final Season Trailer 2 and the Stranger Things 5 Official Teaser, delivering darker stakes, emotional reunions, and the return of the Upside Down’s deadliest threat, Vecna. With anticipation at an all-time high, viewers around the world are searching for every detail connected to the Stranger Things Final Trailer and the final showdown ahead.

The cast—Millie Bobby Brown, Finn Wolfhard, Noah Schnapp, Caleb McLaughlin, Sadie Sink, Gaten Matarazzo, Maya Hawke, Joe Keery, Natalia Dyer, Charlie Heaton, Cara Buono, Winona Ryder, and David Harbour—returns for their biggest fight yet, alongside Jamie Campbell Bower as Vecna. Fan-favorite characters like Chief Hopper, Eleven, Mike Wheeler, Dustin, Lucas, Max, Jonathan Byers, Joyce Byers, Will Byers, and Steve Harrington take center stage as the Hawkins crew prepares for war. Netflix is setting the stage for a massive finale, supported by global excitement around the Stranger Things Trailer, St5 Trailer, and every new look released.

Trailer communities such as Rotten Tomatoes TV, Teaser PRO, FilmSpot Trailer, MovieGasm, KinoCheck, EmergencyAwesome, and IGN TV Trailer, along with countless TV Promos, continue to break down every frame. With growing interest in Stranger Things Season 5 Volume 2, the Stranger Things Season 5 Volume 2 Trailer, Stranger Things Season 5 Part 2, the Stranger Things Season 5 Part 2 Trailer, and the evolving narrative teased in the Stranger Things 5 Trailer Volume 2, fans are preparing for a finale that promises to be unforgettable. This is the final battle for Hawkins—and the world is watching.

snippet.title: George Michael - Careless Whisper (Traducida al Español)
snippet.description:
George Michael - Careless Whisper (Traducida al Español)
espero que les haya encantado el vídeo ❤️

⭐️ sigue mi playlist en Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/playlist/56fC0eaKudzJmw0aZZL7qW?si=df74b108cf2c4394

⭐️ sígueme en mis otros canales:
❥Aureal II: https://www.youtube.com/@aurealii
❥slowed aureal: https://www.youtube.com/@slowedaureal
❥Aureal Sounds: https://www.youtube.com/@aurealsounds4205

---------💙---------
📥 promo: aurealytb@gmail.com
---------💙---------

LYRICS
[Intro]
Oh, woah, woah, oh

[Verse 1]
I feel so unsure
As I take your hand and lead you to the dance floor
As the music dies, something in your eyes
Calls to mind a silver screen and all its sad goodbyes

[Chorus]
I'm never gonna dance again
Guilty feet have got no rhythm
Though it's easy to pretend
I know you're not a fool
I should have known better than to cheat a friend
And waste the chance that I'd been given
So I'm never gonna dance again
The way I danced with you, oh

[Verse 2]
Time can never mend
The careless whispers of a good friend
To the heart and mind, ignorance is kind
There's no comfort in the truth, pain is all you'll find

[Chorus]
I'm never gonna dance again
Guilty feet have got no rhythm
Though it's easy to pretend
I know you're not a fool
I should have known better than to cheat a friend (Shoulda known better, yeah)
And waste the chance that I'd been given
So I'm never gonna dance again
The way I danced with you, oh

[Post-Chorus]
Never without your love

[Instrumental Break]

[Verse 3]
Tonight, the music seems so loud
I wish that we could lose this crowd
Maybe it's better this way
We'd hurt each other with the things we want to say
We could have been so good together
We could have lived this dance forever
But now, who's gonna dance with me?
Please stay

[Chorus]
And I'm never gonna dance again
Guilty feet have got no rhythm
Though it's easy to pretend
I know you're not a fool
I should have known better than to cheat a friend
And waste the chance that I'd been given
So I'm never gonna dance again
The way I danced with you, oh

[Instrumental Break]
[Outro]
(Now that you're gone) Now that you're gone
(Now that you're gone) Was what I did so wrong, so wrong
That you had to leave me alone?

#GeorgeMichael #CarelessWhisper

Paroles et musique : Thomas & Benjamin Pouzin 
©Glorious pop édition 2025

Message de noël :

"Cet album de Noël n’est pas seulement une playlist pour le mois de décembre. Non. C’est une déclaration. Chaque chanson est un rappel que l’espoir n’est pas mort, que la joie n’est pas éteinte, que la lumière brille encore dans les ténèbres.

Quand tu écoutes ces chants, nous voulons que tu entendes plus qu’une mélodie. Nous voulons que tu entendes une promesse. La promesse que l’enfant né dans une crèche est aussi le Roi qui règne aujourd’hui.

Alors, pendant que tu ouvres cet album, ouvre aussi ton cœur. Parce que ce n’est pas juste de la musique de Noël. C’est une invitation à voir Jésus au milieu de ton hiver, à croire que même dans la nuit la plus froide, il y a une chaleur qui vient de l’intérieur."

Benjamin et Thomas - Glorious

Violan alto: Camille Dubois

Message de noël :

"Cet album de Noël n’est pas seulement une playlist pour le mois de décembre. Non. C’est une déclaration. Chaque chanson est un rappel que l’espoir n’est pas mort, que la joie n’est pas éteinte, que la lumière brille encore dans les ténèbres.

Quand tu écoutes ces chants, nous voulons que tu entendes plus qu’une mélodie. Nous voulons que tu entendes une promesse. La promesse que l’enfant né dans une crèche est aussi le Roi qui règne aujourd’hui.

Alors, pendant que tu ouvres cet album, ouvre aussi ton cœur. Parce que ce n’est pas juste de la musique de Noël. C’est une invitation à voir Jésus au milieu de ton hiver, à croire que même dans la nuit la plus froide, il y a une chaleur qui vient de l’intérieur."

snippet.title: On a 24h pour Sortir de ce Labyrinthe INFINI sur Minecraft..
snippet.description:
Cette map réalisée par "OALZ" est inspirée du film "Le Labyrinthe" ("MAZERUNNER" en VO), sorti en 2014.

Avec mes amis @darteuh @Laylo et @Minoc on a décidé de s'y échapper mais le truc c'est que tous les soirs, les portes du labyrinthe se ferment, et on a AUCUNE idée de ce qu'il se passe derrière ces murs...
Ce qui rend ce challenge compliqué c'est que nous sommes en hardcore, ce qui veut dire que toute mort est définitive (ou presque...)

Pour que vous vous rendez compte, voici quelques statistiques sur la map:
🡺 Taille: 3000x3000 blocks
🡺 Total Blocks: 3,861,000,000
🡺 180h de travail

La map est disponible gratuitement juste ici:
https://www.planetminecraft.com/project/mazerunner-x-by-oalz

Map: OALZ
Musiques: EpidemicSound
Montage: Moi
Miniature: BENII21

Un film qui m'a touché récemment: "Mishima: A Life in Four Chapters"
(la musique est composée par Philip Glass et c'est un chef d'œuvre)

Viens me follow ici bg: 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/wyktaurr/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/wyktaur1
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/wyktaur
Discord: https://discord.gg/JKBNXypmqP

Abonnés: 291 653

snippet.title: Événement Heure Zéro - Fortnite Battle Royale [4K 60FPS]
snippet.description:
Rediffusion complète de l’événement narratif Heure Zéro qui a eu lieu le 29 novembre à 20h00 sur Fortnite Battle Royale. (événement en direct de la fin du chapitre 6)
Via: https://www.fortnite.com/news/fortnite-zero-hour-chapter-finale-live-event-on-november-29
#event #fortnite #chapitre7  

00:00 début
02:10 event
14:45 fin

Me soutenir : 
- Code créateur : LVP
PartenaireEpic
- Twitter : https://twitter.com/vieux_pere_

Veuillez noter que j'ai personnellement enregistré le gameplay à l'aide d'une carte d'acquisition elgato 4K60 Pro MK.2 sur Xbox Series X puis édité cette vidéo avec Sony Vegas pro 17 et Adobe Photoshop, ce style unique et exclusif est créé par moi-même.
L’ensemble de ce processus prend de nombreuses heures et j’investis une part importante de mon temps dans la production de contenu, d'aide et de divertissements de haute qualité pour mon public. Bien que d'autres vidéos similaires existent sur YouTube, celle-ci est vraiment unique, toutes les ressemblances étant attribuées à la popularité de Fortnite et à la tendance commune du contenu similaire les jours de mise à jour.
